parts.Short: Thick and plated bonestuff curves to its host shape.

parts.Short: Hundreds and hundreds of fossilized hairs crown the body in a protective coat.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A pair of bone extrusions trenched with grooves race to a symmetrical point above the head.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A gene-sharpened bone spike pierces the crown.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: An addendum of adamantine skull crowns the head in lithophilic regency.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Bone fractals burst from the dome in broad and stunning display.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The growth hex of time has sculpted sharp bonestuff in corkscrew tension.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Iron hooks were fastened to residual leg limbs to provide a graceless, scraping locomotion for their wearer.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A preening tool curves out the skull at the painter's angle and is dotted with a pair of breathing motes.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A flat beak for spooning mud draws out the lower face.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A beak thins to a long point for pecking through shell and bone.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A cluster of pluming feathers draw out the shape of the face in splendid color.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A long and fine beak tube narrows to a point for piercing the flower moat and sucking nectar.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Spaded palms and long claws are shaped to loosen earth and shovel it away.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Crystalline flames crack and lap at the shimmering air.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Wool was dyed in a bath of dreadroot and iron salt, and then woven to warm broad shoulders.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The aching earth belched a ribbon of molten glass onto the Black Stair and anointed a nonet of gas-eating flax-wearers.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: It's a length of salt-sucked skin cut from a goat, or tomb ferret, and it's powdered with the white dust of the dead.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A coarse flax waist is cinched with a watervine hemp rope.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Particulate from the eons-sheared shale sticks in the fibers of goat wool. They make red freckles on the garment.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Ropes of wool are woven in the angled bands of the tartan. They burnish in rich reds, greens, iron greys and sable.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Rough boar wool is cut to an imprecise semi-circle for throwing over a sun-bleached shoulder in a pinch.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Its fine white sheep's wool creases are soiled with the sticky loess of the broad-shouldered world.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Boar hide was brined, limed, and put in a tanning drum. It was cut and fitted into an apron, and now it's a brown canvas for knife scars and tong burns.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Rough tight-spun yard balloons at the calf but cinches at the ankle. The heft of the textile weighs the wide straps down.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Billets of shaved dogwood contour to the breasts, waist, and thigh. The husk is beetle-eaten.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Boiled goat leather was cut to a cuirass and fit with straps and iron buckles. It smells of beeswax.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The reedy guts of an ivy tangle were ripped out, laced, and gilded with an embroidered sash.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Ancient and inscrutable pegs of chrome fished from the trash sea stud thick wedges of boiled goat leather.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A scratchy kirtle was taken to a pocket seamstress and accoutered for cave delving and trinket fishing.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: An apron is pocked with carbon craters the color of the light-sucking void, a thing dreamed by sophists who watched the stars race toward their excluded middle.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Linen was cut to body shape and put in a dye bath of dicalyptus leaves and iron shavings to achieve a chromish luster.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Rough and itchy flax was coarsely threaded, cut to shape, and cinched by a hemp rope.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A leather shirt is mantled with sewn-in loops of steel.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A shiny mesh of linked loops that were sourced from the steel heart of the trash sea.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Cane-beat steel is shaped to the pectorial lunes and stitched to an undergarment of padded goat leather.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A vest of mingled fungusfill cut from the molt of a chitinous jungle cat has been painted and glazed lucid.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A bolt of stretchy, spun fabric was cut to a bodysuit for sneaking.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Fabrics from across the plateau -- quilted eiderdown, weave-of-brinestalk, sticky elastyne -- have been dyed and sewn to a jacket of colored chaos.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Nicked folding metal of dull azure is shaped to the pectorial lunes and stitched to an undergarment of padded goat leather.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Cloth was dyed in a bath of dicalyptus leaves and iron shavings to achieve a chromish luster and then tailored to a ruffled shoulder-skirt.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A swathe of elastyne is sheer-stretched over a cuirass of semi-hard plastic, forming a suit of maneuverable mail.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Blinding light shines off the slick and stretchy suit of vulcanized sap and creates a postpartum amniotic sac.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A cuirass of gas-caught foam stiffens instantaneously when pressure is applied. Its karst surface is dusted with the colorful abrasions of chiliads and the chemical reactions they produce; the material has careened past the outer rings of its expected lifetime and into the unknowing void.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A cuirass of gas-caught foam stiffens instantaneously when pressure is applied. Its karst surface is arrayed with tube sleeves and dusted with the colofur abrasions of chiliads and the chemical reactions they produce; the material has careened past the outer rings of its expected lifetime and into the unknowing void.

parts.Name: ReduceEnergyCosts
parts.ScopeDescription: the energy cost to apply an injector

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Rubber tubes worm their way through salvaged elastyne filted with filters to recover wastewater from the overworked body.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Goat leather is vertipacked with a stratum of loam and the seedlings are nourished to make a walking bush.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Hyperdense metal in meteor black was superheated and banged to the shoulder and chest shapes.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Flakes shaved off a big wedge of the gravid metal have been heat-fused to some kind of animal leather.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Blast furnaces sucked the tidal energy out of the planet, heated carbon to solar temperatures, and poured it into hexagonal molds. The emerald tongs used to retrieve the casts atomized and vented vanadium -- the green glint -- into the manifold, imperfecting the metal and conferring its characteristic hue.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The manifold fibers are colorful and have a touching texture like no other fabric. A molecular weft was pulled through shrinking warps on a fractal loom.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Tetraglass tubes of coolant and antifreeze snake their way over the keg-mail's compressors, and condenser and evaporator coils spin out the shoulders like grandfather trees above the insulation shrub.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Dyed crysteel canisters are fitted to a backrack. Their valves pop out of flux pressurizers, and a splay of hoses allow for several input flows.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Blast furnaces sucked the tidal energy out of the planet, heated carbon to solar temperatures, and poured it into hexagonal molds. The emerald tongs used to retrieve the casts atomized and vented vanadium -- the green glint -- into the manifold, imperfecting the metal and conferring its characteristic hue. Casts mottled with dust particles were culled and fed to lithovores, leaving only the perfect hexagonal prisms.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A dense mesh of dilated tetraglass tubes convey coolant and antifreeze over the keg-mail's jumbo compressors. Blower motors drone a low hum, and condenser and evaporator coils spin out the shoulders like grandfather trees above the insulation shrub.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A calcerous shell was whittled to a hoop dress. Its whorls impress the eye with pleasing geometry before swerving to uncomfortable and dizzying disharmony.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Quark-gluon plasma rapidly cooled and was extinguished on the voidpeaks of the early universe, except where the globules got trapped in 6D kinks of spacetime. There they glided in the slipstream for billions of years until beings discovered them, built machines to extract and cool them, and reheat them in their stellar furnaces.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Wool of many colors was horse-bought from the dromads and sourced beyond the Pale Sea and its great pan of salt. Once the Issachar spun it to yarn on the wheel, a marsh dweller hand-knotted the tzitzit.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Coarse goat wool is dethreading from where brushes have combed out the salt and silicon.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Shorn from the back of a sacred lemur, the hair is laced in a prophet braid.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A silk shoulder drape has been cut and dyed with crushed insects shaved from an oak from the Bowl of Iris.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A shroud of goat leather is circle-stained by the acids of time.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: There is spotted dazzle on the cut hide that brings its bounded strider to pantherine selfhood.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Platinum stitch on a field of salt white brings recognition only to the mirage-trained eyes of the Issachari. The banner has been sewn into a scarlet collar.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Force is pushed across bronze spines through an improbable series of flapping motions, whereupon parasols pop open to catch the mercurial wind.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Hair of unknown origin sticks to the diamond pattern on nylon hip and shoulder straps. Zippered and buttoned pouches allow for the lugging of all the underearth tools one needs.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The crocheted leaf and moss-mass that carpets the hot-smoking yurts of goatfolk has been sewn to a leather collar, giving its wearer the appearance of a creeping bush.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Soft fur is cut from the alabaster pelt of an albino ape into a broad-shouldered cloak.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Bees crawl over the back-mounted slatted rack. A few more dart around nearby.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Shining stitch in the style of circuitry forks down the shoulder fabric.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: An old ropeworking ritual was used to weave a back-worn net of fibrous and supportive straps.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A silvery flowing cloth moves with the lightness of fabric and then hardens in stillness or under the pressure of contact. A light patina is starting to form on the stitch.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A thousand-thread coverture is given its candescent hue by the bluing ore and the harsh light of the Great Desert's foreign and eastern shelf.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Articulated blades unfold to form an aerial screw that gets blown upward by an air thruster mounted below. On activation, the equipper takes flight.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Gloved prosthetic hands attach to the ends of articulating rods. The control mechanism is housed in a false spine box.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Air circulates and the sheet-standard breathes; the edges of the red diamond shrink and lengthen. Blood courses through the arteries of time and into the tissue of the new flesh.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Movement puts the birds stitched into the soft pleats of cloth into stuttery animation.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Prism-studded skin was shorn from a dead monkey and sawed into a cloak.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Slate tubes assemble to scaffold the human form.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Points of discontiguous matter flock in a crescent to a mock wind. Together they bend light across its full spectrum and blur the wearer's torso to a polychrome mess.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Coarse fur is cut from the thickset pelt of an ogre ape into a broad-shouldered cloak.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Cerata pendulate on the cape like prism grass of a windy meadow. They mirror rich hues in cerulean, ruby, star orchid, and void; together they shine to resplendent effect.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Electrodes shine on the lattice across the uuflax weave. Sleeves, widened in fashion, display the gold and cyan heraldic circuitry.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A gargantuan slab of burned and rolled chrome was unjointed from an earth-mover. It shadows its monstrous wielder like a starsail.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Twigs from the witching tree are pared and twisted to a garland for hindsun.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The crown is crushed by wear into a hundred papery creases, and the brim is stained in the fractal signatures of sweat and salt.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: In wool paper and acrylic the pain of experience is smoothed away into the uniform child's cone. Arterial clamps peek out from the interior surface. The cone is fastened by a brass chain, adorned by beads of glass, and branded on the apex with the Holy Rhombus, a sign of the price of innocence.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A leather wrap for the skull is stitched in the brimless style for those who prefer fitting into cracks over shading the jeweled eye.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Red lace wreathes the face to accent the sun-gladdened cheeks of a vintner's wife.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A hideous beak cants over the brain cavity and shades the face in the frightening light of a dim and aching sun.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A second skull was raised as a cone from a sheet of desulfurized metal. Tiny initials are scratched in.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A cap of gunk material that arconauts call black stretch was fished from rubber grottos and stuck to the scalp.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A spiral cavemouth of xanthous shell armors the head while only minorly impairing vision.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Soft fur is cut from the alabaster pelt of an albino ape into a tam with earflaps.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A wearable square is modeled on the bricklayer's mortar board and decorated with a colored tassel.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A hole-cut sheet of steel links fits over the head and neck.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The moss-strewn antlers of some great elk appear to have grown through an ageless, leather helm.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The moss-strewn antlers of some great elk appear to have grown through an ageless, leather helm.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A halogen light sits affixed to a leather head strap.

parts.Name: Description

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A fluted visor is satcheled in strands of tungsten filament. Two antennae coil out the temples in robotic likeness.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The stone-dented metal of aging dusk wraps the brain in a second skull.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Prism-studded skin was shorn from a dead monkey and sawed into a hat.

parts.Short: Airy thoughtstuff was deposited by the pressure of the material realm into a jellified substance and curled into a cirlet. It's bejeweled with crystalline microlife, symbiotes hatched in the thick of the psychic sea.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text: Failed psychic attacks against you cause the attacker to hemorrhage.

parts.Short: A calcerous shell was chopped off at the tip. Its whorls impress the eye with pleasing geometry before swerving to uncomfortable and dizzying disharmony.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A crinkle-sheet of papery metal pokes at the angle of repose.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Tetraxenonoglass blueshifts light hitting the outer shell. On the inner side, electromagnets excite a lining of star mollusk tissue to create the perfect psychic accoustics.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Cloth in the sunbanning hue of salt sight is folded snug to the fit of head and neck.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The sun beams on soapstone with cheeks made high and proud of ochre and teeth. The shadow of a noon canopy bespeaks a treeline thicker with leaflife than any on the plateau or at all north of Moghra'yi.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The moon scowls on an unseen jungle, the craters of brow shaded with animal ash and eaten to a natural ridgeline by the venomous breathe of gods.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Hot fire on soapstone bleeds into damp night at a twilight terminus drawn in blood. The mask wearer assumes this and all dualities.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: In wool paper and acrylic the pain of experience is smoothed away into the aspect of a child. Neuronal clamps peek out from the concave interior surface. The mask is fastened by a brass chain, adorned by beads of glass, and branded on the forehead with the Holy Rhombus, a sign of the price of innocence.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Chrome-brass rings and swarths of leather are precisely cut from a tinker's stencil, but the real signature is on the glass: a scatter of speck-sized fractures from the high salt gales.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Light flecks break themselves on the silver moat and rush back to their place of origin. The signifier becomes the signified; the simulacrum is realized.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Focus-ringed binoculars read the tells of infrared light and produce a textured picture of eye-warm greens.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A folded triangle pouch of burlap was impregnated with vinewood sap to absorb noxious vapor.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A durable plastic mask has been fitted with a simple filter to protect against noxious gas.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Curved glass caps the narrowest in a series of concentric brass tubes. The widest one is fitted with a leather head-strap.

parts.Name: Toolbox
parts.BehaviorDescription: Grants a bonus to identifying artifacts as if your Intelligence score were increased by 5.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Two almonds of glass sit in wireframe cups and resharpen the world's edges.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The hoops sport rhombic facets that reflect light at wavelengths between plum and quartz.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Silver was melted and cast to a perfect sphere in isomorphic veneration of the Kasaphescence.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The glass lune is showered in information across the electromagnetic channels.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short:
Visual Instrument and Sensory Augmentation (G Edition)

Data is painted back and forth between the glass lunes of visor and wristlet. Whereas the outer trim shines gold on F Edition, on this model it fades to grey.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Ring-molds on the laminated metal frame collect ambient sensory data and use it to augment the viewing frustum.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text:
Grants night vision.
You can see two spaces beyond the first occluding object in your line of sight.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Quickened dreamstuff swells to tidal forces and electrifies the membrane of the rondure. It gives off smoke in marble.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Geometry swims across the crystal diodes of the mask. Its expression is smiling in the hypnagognic key.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Glass arches cut and fished from the trash sea have been paired by palette and cored into beads. They've been hung on a dried strand of goat gut and bartered up and down the River Svy.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A glass lens encages a magnetized needle and sits inside a leather wristband.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Miniature airfoil blades spin on the circular face and blow gentle air.

parts.Name: TemperatureAdjuster
parts.BehaviorDescription: Provides a small amount of cooling.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A slender cut of brass was forged in a serpentine crucible and painted with the vexing stripes of nature.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: This simple arm brace is crafted from boiled boar leather and tied on with braided lace. The strips of protective hide are designed to redirect glancing blows to the arm and protect poor archers from their own errant bowstrings.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: It's a shifting minichart of lifesign voltages picked up in the heat and sound signatures of nearby fauna.

parts.Name: Description

parts.Short: On the wrist mount, echo-shaped models in three dimensions expose the structural irregularities of simple inanimate objects nearby.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Gridlines and a red dot are painted on the glass lune, and simple rectangles depict the once-ordered streets of chromium that've since burst like gnarled roots through space and time.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A knitted sleeve warms itself through contact static.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Slick grease-stuff coats the hexagonally-arranged pores across the surface of the metal torus. There's a push cap for lubricant refills.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Hieroglyphs of fluctation are incised on the inner surface of this shiny metal torus.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Plutonic metal is etched with a two-dimensional projection of the rhombic dodecahedral honeycomb, allowing it to snap onto the ley lines of the local region.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Bars partition the bangle clasp into three bands; a cobalt button summons the rest of the quartet.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A dial clicks at right intervals on the metal wrist, and mercurial silver courses through tubework along the plastifer sleeve.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Handwear cut from the hides of down-canyon boars and worn by brinecutters to guard against the briars of the stalk.

parts.Name: Description

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Boar leather vamps are scuffed with little fissures sparking in wind-rasped quartz.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A pair of strapped shoes are cracked on the soles in sinelike patterns of gravel walking.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Scutes are arranged like stony pikes around the apron of the shoe. Light reflects off the enamel shine.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A cord of gold wire fished from the computing guts of the underearth lace the shoe-tailored leather of a dead boar.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: From welt to shank under the ink-smudged boot, a thin plate of magnetized nickel force-welds the wearer to the iron loam.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A canyon pearl fastens sandal straps embroidered in the syncretic imagery of swiftwater nymphs. Like the glacier flow itself, the veneration of Calypso moved with the mystai down the sundered honeycomb and in through the shale fissures beneath the olive mount. There it fractured into the mysteries of the many-named wives, where the memory of freshwater became more faceted than its smooth surface of origin.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Leather boots are steeled by extruded wire meticulously curled into hundreds of chain links.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Steel bands bearing their prying scars have been riveted to a pair of pleated boar leather boots.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A swath of gunk material that arconauts call black stretch was fished from rubber grottos and stuck to the feet.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Nicked folding metal of dull azure bands a pair of lake-fished boots.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Some clever tinker has fused a spring-loaded tendon around each boot to mimic the gait of a large, sprinting bird.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text: As long as you have worn this item for at least 100 rounds, you sprint at thrice your movement speed.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Steel bands bearing their prying scars have been riveted to a pair of pleated boar leather boots. Their soles have been smeared with sliding wax swabbed off the hydraulic presses of the Eaters' tomb.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A pair gas-caught foam sneaks stiffen instantaneously when pressure is applied. Their karst surfaces are dusted with the colorful abrasions of chiliads and the chemical reactions they produce; the material has careened past the outer rings of its expected lifetime and into the unknowing void.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Silver wire cinches a feathery cut of skin from the ghostly yeshyr, hunted in the orchard ruins north of Odrum. They are fastened by a smoking pearl.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Welded bands of aging dusk shield the legs but weigh their wearer to the earth like ore.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The ankle is cinched by a leather strap and goldleaf buckle; crushed plant matter soils the soles.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The finned and wheeled boot had become the sigil of several sects of socionauts by the Late Sultanate. For decades their progenitors careened through the capsule pipelines of the slouching arcology, dismantling it plate by plate, pursued by the constabulary but ferried by their skates to the safety of their moss-skirted hideouts. The metaphor was writ large on the glass guts of the city: Scorch the past. Rocket into the future.

parts.Name: TemperatureAdjuster
parts.BehaviorDescription: Heats up the area around the wearer when in operation.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Blast furnaces sucked the tidal energy out of the planet, heated carbon to solar temperatures, and poured it into hexagonal molds. The emerald tongs used to retrieve the casts atomized and vented vanadium -- the green glint -- into the manifold, imperfecting the metal and conferring its characteristic hue.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Calligraphs are incised in uneven rows and columns that meander across the quarter and back stay of the boot. Their character mass appears to orbit a central statement: "The path is contracted." The rest of the script is etched in a variety of signs and styles that offer competing and composite interpretations of the cryptic proclamation.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Blast furnaces sucked the tidal energy out of the planet, heated carbon to solar temperatures, and poured it into hexagonal molds. The emerald tongs used to retrieve the casts atomized and vented vanadium -- the green glint -- into the manifold, imperfecting the metal and conferring its characteristic hue. Casts mottled with dust particles were culled and fed to lithovores, leaving only the perfect hexagonal prisms.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A kaleidoscopic tartan textures the tongue and vamp. On the backstay, a diode square displays the image of a morphing wall.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Ur-metal strips on the soles are magnetized by bosonic coils, producing a continuous ribbon of negative-mass bubbles that repel the wearer upward.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Cerata pendulate on the shoe tips like the Beetle Moon curled through fog. They mirror rich hues in cerulean, ruby, star orchid, and void; together they shine to resplendent effect.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Quark-gluon plasma rapidly cooled and was extinguished on the voidpeaks of the early universe, except where the globules got trapped in 6D kinks of spacetime. There they glided in the slipstream for billions of years until beings discovered them, built machines to extract and cool them, and reheat them in their stellar furnaces.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A shining jewel, container for gigantic melancholies and gigantic mirths alike, is beset inside a strapped sandal of sheyd leather.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A torso-length lens haloed in refraction waves is suspended in mid air.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A mote of gentle light darts about in the patterns of life.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text:
Emits light in radius 4.
Extinguished permanently when unequipped.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Color swirls around a mote of glow dust.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A phosphorescent opal-like fits in the palm of a hand and glows with the light of auroras absorbed chiliads ago. It floats about preternaturally.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Particles blip off a probabilistic core and appear traced across discrete shells of energy.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: It's a robotic eye lidded by a furcate chassis and embellished with antenna lashes. A minuscule barrel pokes out from its pupil and vibrates. The inner lid is articulated, allowing the drone to scan for incoming projectiles and shoot them down with laser light.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Giant, flattened rings of hypercooled crysteel correlate their wearer to an astronomical body and serve as celestial equator, declination, and meridian. Their edges are filed on a nanon lathe and slice through orbiting debris.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A black particle defies the light-drenched world and charts a helical orbit.

parts.Name: Render
parts.DisplayName: circle of light in the chord of {{agolgot|Agolgot}}

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Minarets of raw bile hue, blackrot, and poison jade wheel about a zeropoint and blur in iridescence to a rainbow of malady.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text:
+1 to all mutation levels
+6 to cybernetics license tier

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: An earthen pot of Svy mud fired in a marsh oven captures a few handfuls from the soil sea and contains them in a bubble world.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Metal frames are mounted on treads to protect against wheel-cramming detritus.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Boartooth beads on the ancient charm are worn to nubs by the cartilage of time, but the flexing cable that holds them together is as strong as the day it was woven. Dangling from the bracelet is a figurine of a deer, carved from a mysterious substance that cracks light like crystal but weighs like metal, producing a shaded lifelikeness elsewhere unseen.

parts.Name: TakenAccomplishment
parts.Text: You recovered the ancestral bracelet of the hindren,
parts.Gospel: At a tavern deep in the wilds of

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A different glyph for 'life' is light-etched on each of its shining chrome segments.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A girdle of ribboned muscle squeezes the wrist and wets it with a burning grease.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text: You take half damage from poison.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Two turrets of sun-conducting chrome cap cylinders of burning gas, which straddle a metal trellis of spades girding some sort of guild mark. A 6-helix of fume, signature of the star engine this flier is wrought through, twirls toward the sky.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text:
You may activate this item to start dashing.
 While dashing, whenever you move in a direction, you dash up to 20 spaces toward the nearest enemy or obstacle and perform an attack.
 For every three spaces you dash, you get +2 to hit and +2 to penetration rolls.

parts.Name: TakenAccomplishment
parts.Text: The Sky-Bear flies anew! From the clutches of the frozen past, you recovered
parts.Hagiograph: The hot, wet breath of the underearth defossilized the Sky-Bear and apprised us of this truth:

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Once-familiar paper, paint, and beads are rearranged to a beastly shape. Pale lights of Spindle color gleam in the eye sockets, and a wicked beak opens in menacing stillness. Across the visage brass chains fasten the pieces of torn innocence that craft the Murmur.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A starless, triangular prism of black glass holds still.

parts.Name: TakenAccomplishment
parts.Text: You clutched the black glass of the
parts.Gospel: While wandering in the jungle near Kyakukya,

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Sharp points are run through with bright and brilliant amethyst and sapphire. The colors remain but smolder to heather in their dying light. The chime is grave-still.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Byzantine purple smolders at a medium hue on the sharp and linked prisms of the crystal. It hums with new life and ingenuity.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text: Grants you Quicken Mind: refresh a random cooldown on use.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A curtain of thrumming cables make a mantle for hunched shoulders. They pitch at neuronal frequencies long dormant.

parts.Name: Toolbox
parts.BehaviorDescription: When powered, this item grants a 40% chance that a tinkered item will have a random item modification. This may include item modifications that aren't normally tinkerable.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A thorn crown arranged of crystals at telling psionic angles make a landmark in the psychic sea.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A ribbed cable of tangent needle points squeezes the limb and quickens its biomatter beyond expectation.

parts.Name: IntPropertyChanger
parts.BehaviorDescription: Wearer may take any action while sprinting at no additional penalty.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Shining jewels are scattered across the contours of a galactic visage, and edges drawn between them sketch the outline of a sashed Fool. Far away at the chrome crest, beads of bright and searing light suggest the shape of a medial ewer, and beyond its spout, a vast and timeful structure. The inside of the mask is ribboned with burnt tracery from where it was molded on a gallium lathe, then dyed with the milked irises of shedim and set to dry in a pool of warm static.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text:
+1 to all mutation levels
+6 to cybernetics license tier

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Burning rubies, carnelians, and garnets are arranged as a warm and giving sun. Diminutive rocky orbs pass by in the near space of the visage, and in the far space a prism of freight lengthens into a wider void. The inside of the mask is ribboned with burnt tracery from where it was molded on a gallium lathe, then dyed with the milked irises of shedim and set to dry in a pool of warm static.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: On the countenance, ribbons of alabaster cloud circumscribe a lapis sea and forests of jade. At the median of it all, a Spindle pierces the outer rondure and disappears beyond the composition. A second obstructed spire, what must be the Spindle's shadow, soaks up the light thrown off by the southern sky of crystal white. The inside of the mask is ribboned with burnt tracery from where it was molded on a gallium lathe, then dyed with the milked irises of shedim and set to dry in a pool of warm static.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Jasper rocks break on the edges of the mask and hem in a pale sea of milky quartz. The Spindle bisects the wide Face, and symmetry blooms beneath it. The inside of the mask is ribboned with burnt tracery from where it was molded on a gallium lathe, then dyed with the milked irises of shedim and set to dry in a pool of warm static.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A single mount of inlaid basalt and malachite splays open; an image of the Spindle blossoms from its center and dominates the festooned aspect. The inside of the mask is ribboned with burnt tracery from where it was molded on a gallium lathe, then dyed with the milked irises of shedim and set to dry in a pool of warm static.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A bowed lune is cracked from where it was smashed off the gallium lathe. The shedim had no eyes left to color the dim and final Face, and it lay too long discarded in a pool of warm static. The sultanate is broken.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: All-color nacre is hardened into an ontologically perfect shape; the mathematics of spheres are mere approximations. Inside, ribboned patterns of aether are frozen in stasis and cohere as a moonlit vista, a scene somehow tethered to the spacetime point whence you observed it. The meaning of this pairing is unknown and unknowable.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text:
+40 psychic glimmer
Objects you find are five times more likely to come from other dimensions.

parts.Name: TakenAccomplishment
parts.Text: You clutched
parts.Hagiograph: O! Our hearts turned to stellar remnants when

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A gigantic whorl lip snapped off the driving wheel of culture, fell out of its star vault's orbit, and, through the eroded methods of time, arrived here. Astroexotic spores lash its metasteel underrim, pilgrims from a hot fungal core biding time between now and some mystifying future point.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A blooming kitesail of extrasolar flax is knitted on battens to catch the poison air of some faraway swamp planetoid and power an ecumenical cycle. Its clews are stitched with syncretic plethora from across the dreaming gamut.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A giant clockface is traced with lemniscates to gauge the entheogenic pressures building in abyssal sun cores. The priest of the machine who took its readings and sung the dial left is indebted to the distant colleague whose klatch invented the whistled language 8000 years later.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text: Berate, Intimidate, and Menacing Stare also confuse per Confusion rank 10.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Spinning the stannic cuboid about any of its axes of rotation generates a pinch of resistance. A wrist strap and gyroscopic frame enable the cell to absorb and store its wearer's kinetic energy.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A toboggan repels above the ground and gently rocks on an ethereal wave. It's encircled by a corona of wafting dust.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A large camel bladder is knotted at the bottom and suspended with a strap of intestine.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text: When worn, liquid in this item doesn't count toward your encumbrance.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Chrome was molded into a canister and fastened with a brass mounting bracket.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Collagen was molded into a liquid vessel.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Rime-dotted nodules crust over the infected skin, where an algid mist clings. The fungus colony has terraformed the epidermis into what looks like a miniature range of ice-capped peaks.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Tiny spore-motes flutter down from the fleshy gills that twitch on the striated skin. Trapped inside are another thousand spores waiting to be jostled free.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Dozens of tiny mouths tessellate the infected skin, their moist lips pursing in asynchronicity and panting out prattle. Every so often, the cacophony harmonizes into sensible speech.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A wax-weeping fungus has encased the appendage in a lucent cast. Body heat melts the innermost layer, and a thick, waxy milk sloshes against its hardened prison.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Tapered lobes of cross-dimensional fungus flesh tap a center growth to the sequence of the prime numbers. Inside, sporelife readies for puffing.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: This patch of furry skin is painted with dried blood.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Leather scraps were cut from a wider swath for some unknown leatherworking project.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: The leather bracer frays where it was ripped open.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: This leather bracer is striated with streaks of dried body-salt, the marks of heavy use.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: It's a robotic half-eye lidded by a furcate chassis and embellished with antenna lashes. A minuscule barrel pokes out from its pupil and vibrates. The inner lid is articulated, allowing the drone to scan for incoming projectiles and shoot them down.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Wet rings of shuddering muscle shrink and spew body broth in peristaltic waves.

parts.Name: Render
parts.DisplayName: circle of light in the chord of {{ehalcodon|Ehalcodon}}

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Minarets of starburst ejecta from the proto-universe wheel about a zeropoint and blur in the iridescence of a nondeterministic God.

parts.Name: RulesDescription
parts.Text:
+1 to all mutation levels
+6 to cybernetics license tier

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: When a song of power roars out the moted forest and slides up Worldskin, the sidewise veil shields the sorceress's ears and eyes.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: Microscopic needlework on the sleeve encodes the entire history of the crystal sphere and Great Moon, at least from the fey perspective. In the well of kingdom and castle, the embroidered texture returns the pressure of a gloved hand locked in dance at the masquerade ball.

parts.Name: Description
parts.Short: A cameo of meteorite sardonyx bears an unknown clan sigil in florid script, serifed with tiny gears and sails.
